{"tid":1795901,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］紅磡火車站及灣仔行人天橋全部加上密孔式鐵絲網！","createTime":"2019-12-24T08:56:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-24T09:10:32.000Z","uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6493fe66e968e270dfbf869c35c4e54b500378dd","tid":1795901,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T08:56:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sz8mJtf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSz8mJtf.jpg&h=35497775&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【鐵網圍封行人天橋】今晚是平安夜，包括紅磡海底隧道在內的多條交通要道上的天橋，都安裝密孔鐵網。<br />\n<br />\n在紅隧九龍出入口、收費廣場上通往理工大學的行人天橋，兩邊通風位置都加裝近兩米高的鐵網，相信防止有人從天橋投擲物件，堵塞紅隧出入口。（相片由讀者提供）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/2724733720945564/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F2724733720945564%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=IuE3y9gLaM%2BC%2BJZgSaDlppKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=73d2bd4c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/2724733720945564/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n灣仔 ： <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://fbwat.ch/1iAUf3CbdkOXlxCR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffbwat.ch%2F1iAUf3CbdkOXlxCR&d=IuE3y9gLaM%2BC%2BJZgSaDlppKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=0a303abc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fbwat.ch/1iAUf3CbdkOXlxCR</a>"},{"pid":"ebec9c3afd66e56bec786bd27f8b0598451f8bfe","tid":1795901,"uid":283428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T09:02:10.000Z","msg":"大老山都加緊"},{"pid":"9972a879895e4a693bb4ca7b8df435803aef4d8a","tid":1795901,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T09:06:32.000Z","msg":"馬場 大學果頭好多天橋都加晒"},{"pid":"09e581a7806c659aa7d36d9f1fc4f23e430b3c8e","tid":1795901,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T09:10:32.000Z","msg":"好岩做連儂牆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}